These are Puzzles for 3x7 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-4-1::.
7 different games are played: go, monopoly, whist, chess, snooker, billiard, backgammon
House: futuristic, art-deco, wooden, modern, farmhouse, tower, cottage
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: badminton, basketball, biathlon, cycling, rugby, surfing, tennis
 1. the person playing backgammon is the tower house##1
 2. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1
 3. the person playing snooker is on the far right##1
 4. the wooden house is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rugby##3
 5. the person playing billiard is the person playing billiard##1
 6. the person who's sport is basketball is the futuristic house##1
 7. the cottage house is on the left or right of the person playing backgammon##3
 8. the modern house is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1
 9. the person playing monopoly is on the left or right of the tower house##3
10. the person playing whist is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1
11. the person playing billiard is in the middle##1
12. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cycling##3
13. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left or right of the art-deco house##3
14. the person playing billiard is in an even position##4
15. the person playing monopoly is on the left or right of the tower house##3
16. the tower house is in an odd position##4
17. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the person playing chess##1
18. the cottage house is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
19. the person who's sport is basketball is the person playing billiard##1
20. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |       2       |    3     |     4      |     5     |    6     |    7     |
| Game      | backgammon  | monopoly | whist | billiard        | go       | chess | snooker     |
| House   | tower   | cottage       | wooden  | futuristic  | modern  | art-deco   | farmhouse  |
| Sport         | tennis | rugby         | surfing  | basketball | badminton | cycling  | biathlon |

