 4. the person eating corn is on the far left or far right##3
 5. the person who likes fuchsia is on the left of the person eating corn##1
 6. the person who likes white is on the left of the person eating banana##1
 7. the person who likes fuchsia is the security-guard##1
 8. the accountant is in an odd position##4
 9. the person eating raspberry is on the right of the person eating lemon##1
10. the person who likes turquise is the accountant##1
11. the writer is on the right of the person who likes fuchsia##1
12. the teacher is on the right of the person who likes turquise##1
13. the person eating peas is on the left or right of the writer##3
14. the lawyer is on the left or right of the person who likes amber##3
15. the pilot is in an even position##4
16. the person eating plum is on the left or right of the person who likes orange##3
17. the person eating peas is in an even position##4
18. the person eating banana is the social-worker##1
19. the pilot is on the left of the lawyer##1
20. the person who likes amber is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
